  "instructions": [
    "Heat vegetable oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat. Add minced garlic and chopped onion.",
    "Sauté for about 1 minute until the onions start to soften.",
    "Add julienned carrot, finely chopped red chili peppers, and green onion to the pan. Stir-fry for another 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in all-purpose seasoning and soy sauce. Mix well.",
    "Gently add dumplings to the stir-fry mixture, cooking until they're fully heated through. This should take about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Toss with bean sprouts before serving."
